<i>Dia tak pakai bantal.</i>

954
01:00:02,227 --> 01:00:04,897
Aku melihatmu berjalan
saat aku berkendara kemari.

955
01:00:06,565 --> 01:00:08,066
<i>Akan kutunjukkan kemampuanku.</i>

956
01:00:08,150 --> 01:00:09,067
<i>Kau tahu siapa aku.</i>

957
01:00:09,151 --> 01:00:11,361
<i>Aku Kang Dan-i.
Aku pernah sukses di periklanan.</i>

958
01:00:11,445 --> 01:00:12,738
<i>Desain sampul oleh Ji Seo-jun.</i>

959
01:00:12,821 --> 01:00:16,199
<i>Dia desainer terbaik. Bawa dia ke Gyeoroo.</i>

960
01:00:16,283 --> 01:00:17,701
<i>Aku melihatnya menangis.</i>

961
01:00:18,368 --> 01:00:20,203
<i>Kukira hatiku akan hancur.</i>

962
01:00:21,204 --> 01:00:22,289
<i>Orang-orang</i>

963
01:00:23,457 --> 01:00:24,583
memanggil namaku.

